    "Users can access attribute definitions and basic data distribution statistics (minimum, maximum, average, and median values) by hovering over pink circular markers.",
    "• Opinion and Prediction Region (Figure 5 (B)) is dedicated to thought elicitation by both users and the AI.-The upper part displays aggregate predictions from both humans and AI.",
